{
  "stem": "3040.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I forced her to step out from the ranks and join the others who were supposed to be left over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told her I will come back for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "These were my words.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The rest of us were marched to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were-- there was a train waiting for us, a cattle train, these boxcars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were shoved in 100 people to a train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were counting everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't let anybody more than 100.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had their own ideas about things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was all-- and once I came into that train, I saw-- I didn't have any illusions as to where the destination of that train is.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I knew there were no facilities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were mixed-- mixed people, old, young, children, infants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Whoever was there from the sick people from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I know this is no good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are not going any place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I walk myself to the corner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "These cattle cars have corners-- have small windows about two by three feet in every corner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I worked myself to be close to that corner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were-- the windows were crisscrossed with barbed wire so that Nobody could escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But at least I wanted to be at the window.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when the train-- and we were standing there on the platform for maybe 5, 6 hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And towards the evening, the train started moving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there were other young people waiting also in that corner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we started to talk that we would like to conceive some kind of a plan how to escape that train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we actually, we have managed to remove that barbed wire from the windows.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
